room_title: Escape room "Pyramid Paradox" by Tick Tock Escape Room in Overland Park
room_description:
While exploring an ancient Egyptian pyramid, your team has accidentally triggered a trap which has blocked your only means of escape! However, there is a fail-safe mechanism which will allow you to exit if you can activate it within an hour. Will you decipher the clues, discover the secret, and escape in time?
Or have you found your final resting place?
